{"tid":850271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粉飾太平！中國趕2020前脫貧 最新進度「1面牆」","createTime":"2018-10-06T10:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T16:11:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":122,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"1070fc834ce33543d68758af8a72cdd55efabe8e","tid":850271,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpIFw8rk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpIFw8rk.jpg&h=a5bbd11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國國家主席習近平宣示要在2020年前讓中國貧戶「脫貧」，地方政府也被要求積極介入輔導，近期內網路上瘋傳一系列「扶貧」照片，官方將各農村貧戶平房的1面牆粉刷如新，但實際情況並沒有改變，被網友笑稱「正港粉飾太平」。<br />\n<br />\n臉書上近期內盛傳幾張照片，從中可見中國貧窮地區農村的平房，面向道路的1側全被官方漆成嶄新模樣，還在空地搭起柵欄種植花草，但屋舍其他地方如屋頂、內牆等從外面較不易發覺的地方，全都還是維持原樣，1名老屋主看似無助地坐在黃土地上。<br />\n<br />\n《多維新聞網》對此查證，透過此系列「扶貧」照片中出現在牆上的電話號碼，可查出照片所在地為山東省日照市，而當地的莒縣、五蓮縣均被中國當局定義為「國家級貧困縣」，雖然高層推動「脫貧」計畫，但窮鄉僻壤貪汙問題嚴重，浮報預算、私吞公帑的事情令中國中央無可奈何。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友知悉此事後，均感到相當不可思議，紛紛留言指出「真是奇觀了，可以整修成這樣」、「簡直是亂搞，跟人民的需求完全脫節」、「陰陽工程」、「地獄鬼國」、「外牆拉皮」、「共產黨專制常作這種毫無意義的事」、「啥都做假有意思嗎？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpSEJpOa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpSEJpOa.jpg&h=7c50b912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpFyQNuP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpFyQNuP.jpg&h=cdce3ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2572403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2572403&d=Lh5EBkH1FGt7o%2BWrmTGuSXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a1e40b0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2572403&h=d46782e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2572403</a>"},{"pid":"dffee97dfc69e5e0ee71d48a2586fd512b6638ca","tid":850271,"uid":47964,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c0bf58b2d5bad85ad136a1fb836531c00f6d6c","tid":850271,"uid":93986,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:56:25.000Z","msg":"落哂格<br />\n人地俾要油全間屋既預算<br />\n佢就油一面"},{"pid":"80ab0535578b6e37e8b065d1d4c497c1cb078e88","tid":850271,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"支爆前夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0bf90e9df2fd79273bb99fcae873631dee2228","tid":850271,"uid":156652,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KyDub8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKyDub8L.jpg&h=e4871db3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83ee4f37bd966b18ca37c34ba72b9b86da3ca912","tid":850271,"uid":25424,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f0d2ce2e903b9773820f09a5f10a17b0ae034e","tid":850271,"uid":39777,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"be9da801361db50e7d0bf006b26e24caa19a1452","tid":850271,"uid":54337,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"有創意，又贏"},{"pid":"fc12bbdb337596602502540bf946b7df41134b3c","tid":850271,"uid":44454,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:0